  Open the local content editor:

  npm run editor

  Then open the localhost address Vite prints. Currently, “טעינת טיוטה” reads content/draft/editor/catalog.json, not the imported blueprint draft. “טעינת מאושר” loads the small
  approved seed catalog.

  To view the current public shell:

  npm run dev

  Open the localhost URL shown by Astro.

  The eventual full workflow will be:

  blueprint
  → npm run content:import-draft
  → correct imported content in the local editor
  → export validated content/approved/catalog.json
  → npm run dev
  → view the complete catalog
