• Test the complete flow like this:

  1. Start the editor:

  npm run editor

  2. Open:

  http://127.0.0.1:4333

  3. In the editor:

  - Load your JSON file, or load a Markdown/text Blueprint document.
  - Edit and resolve validation errors.
  - Under “ייצוא סביבת Bootstrap”, enter a folder name such as:

  catalog-2026-2027

  - Click “ייצוא contents/<folder>/bootstrap.json”.
  - If warnings exist, acknowledge them before exporting.

  4. Confirm this file was created:

  contents/catalog-2026-2027/bootstrap.json

  5. Stop the editor with Ctrl+C, or open another terminal. Start the public site using that Bootstrap:

  npm run dev -- --data=./contents/catalog-2026-2027

  6. Open:

  http://127.0.0.1:4321